sequenceDiagram 
    participant U as User
    participant F as React Frontend
    participant B as Rust Backend
    participant API as Transport API

    U->>F: Open stop page
    F->>B: Request departures for stop
    B->>API: Fetch live data
    API-->>B: Raw transport data
    B->>B: Parse & transform
    B-->>F: Clean departure list
    F-->>U: Render live departures